  ============================================================
  SANKALP LEARNING — ABOUT US PAGE (Editable HTML Version)
  ============================================================
  HOW TO EDIT:
  - Search for text you want to change and replace it directly
  - Numbers/stats: search for the value (e.g. "6,00,000+") and update
  - Colors are controlled by CSS variables at the top of the <style> block
  - To change icons, replace the SVG code inside the icon containers
  ============================================================
